<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_228_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns aber <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt . eẅch von den <expan>lewffe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l4">ʒu Beheim etwas ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıben</expan> etc / Das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l5"><expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır ſeıd der ſchrıft dıe wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l6">nehſt <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> teten . nıht treffenlıchs <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / bıs auf dıſʒ ʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l7">ıſt vns ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der Römıſch etc kunıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l8">
<add>lıg</add> mıt xij<hi rend="sup">M</hi> <expan>gewappent<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>manne<ex>n</ex></expan> . vor der <expan>clöſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> genant Cladrawn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l9">daʒ dıe huſſen nehſt <expan>gewunne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd ſüll der huſſen noch etwie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l10">uıl in <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>cloſt<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein vnd ſey gute <expan>hoffnu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> / daʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> vnſer </ab>
