<add><ab facs="#facs_228_line_1577134335142_2056">daʒ wır <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_228_line_1577134338595_2061">es ſüll ſeinen </ab><ab facs="#facs_228_line_1577134341783_2066"><expan>künıgl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> an </ab><ab facs="#facs_228_line_1577134345533_2071">dem ort wol geen </ab></add> / Auch ıſt vns geſagt <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ dıe huſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l15">der ſloſſ eins genant das Neẅhaws bey Prag belegert <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l17">wıe ſıch aber dıe lewff hınfür machen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . <expan>Dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> wıſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_r1l19">wır yecʒ nıht <expan>ʒuſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_228_line_1577134398900_2111"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> Jnuocauıt </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_228" id="113r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
